{
  "info": {
    "name": "Health Portal API",
    "description": "All backend endpoints for the health-portal monorepo.\n\n- Admin routes (`/api/patients`, `/api/appointments`, `/api/prescriptions`) are **unauthenticated**.\n- Portal routes (`/api/portal/*`) require a session cookie set by `POST /api/auth/login`.\n\nPostman's cookie jar handles `hp_session` automatically. An `X-Session-Id` header fallback is supported server-side if you prefer header-based auth.\n\n**Happy-path run order** (folder is provided at the bottom):\n1. `Auth / Register (POST /api/patients)`\n2. `Auth / Login`\n3. `Auth / Me`\n4. `Appointments / Create`\n5. `Prescriptions / Create`\n6. `Portal / *` (summary, appointments, prescriptions, refills)\n7. `Auth / Logout`\n8. `Negative / Portal without session` (should 401)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4000" },
    { "key": "patientId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "appointmentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "prescriptionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "loginEmail", "value": "jane.doe@example.com" },
    { "key": "loginPassword", "value": "password123" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/health",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('envelope ok', () => {",
                  "  const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(b.success).to.equal(true);",
                  "  pm.expect(b.data.status).to.equal('ok');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('patient returned', () => {",
                  "  const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(b.success).to.equal(true);",
                  "  pm.expect(b.data.email).to.equal(pm.collectionVariables.get('loginEmail'));",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('hp_session cookie set', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.cookies.has('hp_session')).to.equal(true);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{loginEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{loginPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/auth/me",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
